{"tid":1576640,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"突發！ 俄病毒研究所大爆炸 內有多種病毒","createTime":"2019-09-17T10:31:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T11:27:39.000Z","uid":32511,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"fc71b938c97f9600d85379e2460a508adc70286b","tid":1576640,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T10:31:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jdJf4rA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjdJf4rA.jpg&h=fd51592a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nOne of the world&rsquo;s largest virus research centers, located in Siberia, was<br />\nreportedly engulfed in flames after a sudden explosion rocked the secretive<br />\ncompound, known for its stores of Ebola, HIV, anthrax and other strains.<br />\n <br />\nFirefighters and rescue services were scrambled on Monday to respond to a<br />\nfire that broke out in Koltsovo, a scientific hub several kilometers from<br />\nNovosibirsk. The situation was quickly upgraded from an ordinary emergency to<br />\na major incident as the explosion and fire affected Russia&rsquo;s research center<br />\nof virology and biotechnology, often referred to as the Vector Institute.<br />\n <br />\nThe laboratory is known for having developed vaccines for Ebola and<br />\nhepatitis, as well as for studying epidemics and genera issues surrounding<br />\nimmunology. During the Cold War, it was thought to be part of now-defunct<br />\nSoviet biological weapons program, meaning that some of the most dangerous<br />\nstrains &ndash; including that of smallpox, Ebola, anthrax and certain plagues &ndash;<br />\nare still being kept inside the Institute&rsquo;s building.<br />\n <br />\nWith that in mind, a local branch of the Emergencies Ministry swiftly<br />\nresponded to the call, sending in 13 fire engines and 38 firefighters, who<br />\nentered the six-story building minutes after arrival.<br />\n <br />\nThe fire was located and quickly extinguished on the fourth floor where some<br />\n&ldquo;construction works&rdquo; were being carried out.<br />\n <br />\nReports by local authorities were conspicuously light on detail, with various<br />\nsources suggesting it was a gas blast that had triggered a fire at the<br />\nconstruction site. One construction worker suffered burns to his legs and was<br />\ntaken to hospital for trauma care.<br />\n <br />\nThe mayor of Koltsovo, for his part, assured the public that there was no<br />\nrelease of hazardous substances in the area. Still, the cause of the blast<br />\nremains unknown and an investigation has been launched.<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n大意:<br />\n一座位在西伯利亞Koltsovo的病毒疫苗研究所建築工事的樓層<br />\n發生了瞬間小爆炸和火警,有工作人員三度灼傷送醫.<br />\n該研究所據信曾經是蘇聯冷戰時期研究生化兵器的據點.<br />\n目前還儲存有很多種類的病毒例如 炭疽 伊波拉 HIV<br />\n還有活體天花病毒(目前世界上只有此處和美國亞特蘭大的疾病管制中心有).<br />\n <br />\n市長表示並沒有任何有害物質洩漏,<br />\n關於爆炸的原因至今不明,已經著手調查中."},{"pid":"55280807b7f2b08cf63db82810b7fe4f36a4afe3","tid":1576640,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T10:32:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yt2HG33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyt2HG33.jpg&h=9fcb0aae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TrPZKfU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTrPZKfU.jpg&h=433e1fe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【922攻略流出】<br />\n907<span style=\"color: gold;\">加強版</span>配合hkmap live <br />\n更「大局」交通測試，彩虹戰衣、影帝、機巴、塞鐵、嶄新突擊RB、私家車傾巢而出，裡應外合 <br />\n+機場員工集體Call Sick <br />\n+雷達站/機場附近新搞作<br />\n+大量中港貨櫃司機加入物資支援！<br />\n<br />\n更多攻略，陸續公布，敬請留意"},{"pid":"5aed9db2598e12117bc2c38b11d4ba74c71db380","tid":1576640,"uid":144996,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T10:34:37.000Z","msg":"俄佬喺班蝗蟲隔離咁耐都冇事<br />\n仲有咩毒會驚啊講真"},{"pid":"18d1cdf809f3dc7dac46e95e6d4183302af2ae88","tid":1576640,"uid":55231,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T10:35:43.000Z","msg":"俄國又豬瘟又痛毒 瘋狂送大禮"},{"pid":"8